Author: Yunsul,
Description: Ariadna Lereg Ilestri Pre Agrigent. And so my life begins with this ridiculously long name, born to royalty and the center of attention — all because of one dangerous man; the veritably insane tyrant king, ruthless conqueror of ten empires, nightmare of all continents… and my father?! Will I be able to survive this maniac?
AlternativeNames: EMPEROR'S ONLY DAUGHTER , KOUTEI NO HITORI MUSUME , 皇帝の一人娘 , 皇帝的独生女 , 황제의 외동딸
